Getting Token for authentication

Request URL :
POST http://{MBIZ_API_HOST}/auth/request

Request - Headers :
    - Content-Type : application/json

Request - Body :
    {
        "public_key": "{PUBLIC_KEY}", // string (diberikan oleh mbiz)
        "user_id": {ID USER}, // integer (diberikan oleh mbiz)
        "scope": "*" // string
    }

